text: Aythorpe Roding is a village and civil parish in Uttlesford, Essex, England. In 2001 there were 201 people living in Aythorpe Roding. Aythorpe Roding is one of The Rodings. There is a postmill in Aythorpe Roding which is the largest in Essex. == References == Category:Uttlesford Category:Villages in Essex Category:Civil parishes in Essex Category:Towns in Essex
